title: [BUG] "register" step does not show the model version in UI

labels.name: area/model-registry
labels.description: Model registry, model registry APIs, and the fluent client calls for model registry

body:

- **Python version**:
- **yarn version, if running the dev UI**:


### Describe the problem


Not able to see registered model version in UI from mlflow.recipes import Recipe


### Tracking information

_No response_

### Code to reproduce issue

 import os

r = Recipe(profile="local")
r.clean()
r.inspect()
r.run("split")
r.run("transform")
r.run("train")
r.run("evaluate")

--> r.run("register")

Model Name: red_wine_classifier

Model Version: 1

Model Source URI: runs:/df1efb172db4463284267a532add15bb/train/model

Run duration (s): 0.783

Last updated: 2022-12-09 17:57:20
